Juventus forward, Cristiano Ronaldo, has reacted to his side’s Serie A 2-0 win over Bologna on Sunday. Ronaldo said Juventus’ win over Bologna was a very important victory, adding that Andrea Pirlo’s men are on the right track. Juventus defeated Bologna at Allianz thanks to two goals from Arthur Melo and Weston Mckennie. The result against Bologna means Juventus are now in the 4th position on the Serie A table with 36 points from 18 games. Reacting, Ronaldo wrote on Twitter after the game, “Very important victory! We are on the right track! Go on like this.” Juventus next game is against SPAL in the Coppa Italia quarter-final on Wednesday.